  <Docs>
    <summary>
            Represents the result of a web search tool invocation by a hosted service.
            </summary>
    <remarks>
            This content type represents the results found by a hosted AI service's web search tool.
            The results contain a list of <see cref="T:Microsoft.Extensions.AI.AIContent" /> items describing the web pages
            found during the search, typically as <see cref="T:Microsoft.Extensions.AI.UriContent" /> instances.
            </remarks>
  </Docs>
